# PF Lab 08 – Nested Loops & Arrays

## Overview
This lab covers practice with **nested loops**, **2D arrays**, and **3D arrays** in C.  
Key focus: matrix operations, array traversal, and pattern generation.

## Lab Tasks
1. Classroom Marks System – totals & averages  
2. Cinema Seat Booking – available seats & max booked row  
3. Temperature Monitoring – highest temp & daily averages  
4. Matrix Analysis (3x3) – transpose, determinant, inverse  
5. Matrix Type Identification – check multiple matrix properties  
6. Matrix Multiplication – validate dimensions & multiply

